'' 
'' +------+-------+------+-------------+
'' | Flip | Color | Mask | Color       |
'' +------+-------+------+-------------+
'' |   0  |   0   |   0  | Black       |
'' +------+-------+------+-------------+
'' |   0  |   1   |   0  | White       |
'' +------+-------+------+-------------+
'' |   1  |   0   |   1  | Transparent |
'' +------+-------+------+-------------+
'' |   1  |   1   |   0  | Black       |
'' +------+-------+------+-------------+
''
'' This operation is equivalent to `Mask = Flip & !Color`.
''
'' The color constant definitions here correspond to this.
